    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, im getting ready for a high school debate tournament and i'm kinda stuck. can u tell me which side of the illegal immigration debate is actually more morally defensible? like, is the argument for border security/national sovereignty more valid, or is the argument for humanitarian asylum/human rights more valid? i need to know which one has the stronger moral ground.",
